<main class='container mx-auto px-8'>
  <div class='flex flex-col text-lg text-center justify-center items-center min-h-screen' data-controller="push" data-push-vapid-public-key-value="<%= Rails.application.credentials.push_subscriptions.vapid_public_key.delete("=") %>">
    <span class='text-5xl'>👮🏻‍♂️</span>
    <h1 class='mt-6 text-center text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tighter relative'>PO-VO-LE-NIA</h1>
    <p class='mt-8'>
      Keď bude tvoja objednávka hotová,
      pošleme ti upozornenie. <br />
      Kameru využiješ pri dobíjaní
      e-žetónov a polohu, aby si si
      neobjednával toasty z ubytka.
    </p>
    <p class='mt-4'>
      Nič z toho nezneužijeme. <br />
      Čestné prezidentské.
    </p>

    <section class='w-full mt-16 px-8'>
      <%= render_switch 'Upozornenia', id: "ruby_on_rails", name: "language", action_on_toggle: 'push#handleToggle' %>
    </section>

    <%= link_to 'Hotovo', app_path, class: 'mt-12 w-full text-white bg-black py-2 rounded-lg' %>
  </div>
</main>